            },
          }),
          // More extensions...
        ]
      }
    })
    ```

3. **Set the Attributes Appropriately**: Whenever you are inserting or updating mentions in the editor, ensure that these attributes are being appropriately set. If you are using a suggestion mechanism, make sure that `workspaceId` and `slug` are included when constructing the mention nodes.

This setup ensures that your mention nodes have the necessary attributes by default and that they will be parsed/rendered correctly when the document is processed. If attributes are missing in elements being created or manipulated, make sure to explicitly set them at those places in your code.
